		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />MMC1 is super common (thus widely supported) and pretty useful.  There are a few MMC1 titles that use 16kB of PRG-RAM (Genghis Khan is one - probably not so widely supported), but I doubt you'll need more than 8kB, right?

		

